name: Memory Leak (piskopat39)
description:
The instruction at 0x00023FB98 referenced memory at 0x000230FB98. The memory could not be written.

    The game starts, main menu appears. You press start, but something is wrong.

 Try clicking again.

Use A-D to move, Space to jump.

Mind your cursor.

Warning : Contains flashing lights.

This game was made solely by me for Magara Game Jam 3 in 72 hours.

Background Music and 2D Assets were made during the jam, sound effects were taken from The Madrooster 2021 Sound Library.

Thanks for playing.
